<section class="philosophy-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="glass-panel manifesto">
        <h2>Filosofía <span class="highlight">Slow Dating</span></h2>
        <p>
          En un mundo de conexiones efímeras, elegimos la permanencia.
          La conexión dura hasta que tú lo decidas. Sin cronómetros. Sin ansiedad.
        </p>
        <div class="stats">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-val">∞</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Tiempo de Match</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-val">100%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Privacidad</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-val">Max 2</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Matches / Día</span>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .philosophy-section {
    padding: var(--section-spacing) 0;
  }

  .manifesto {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-primary), 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-val {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-main);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .stats {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
